Series OUTLINE:
Self contained fan edit films that has a slight hint of a continual storyline that connects each episode, but each Episode is considered a separate fan film set in the same universe. It is a soap opera drama of movies connecting into a bigger storyline or self contained watchable fan edit films. The concept surrounds the Silence Aliens from Doctor Who who try to invade our history through any means possible be it Alien abductions, Alien take overs, spiritual possession, or Alien zombie parasites. As the series continues each episode brings us closer to the silence, but every episode always remains as a self contained fan film.

Synopsis OUTLINE:
HUMANITIES FINAL BATTLE AGAINST THE SILENCE.

This series in a sense is a sequel to the hit 1996 series called "Dark Skies" on NBC which inspired this project to begin with.
Dark Skies TV show was a weekly TV show based around historical events that had a Alien Twist intertwined into history.
My series is kinda similar to this concept: Example: Apollo 11 they find Aliens on the moon"

Eventually the story in later episodes stray away from Dark skies, but I tried to keep this crossover to historical events and time periods. Series starts in the ancient past and works it way up to our current future and beyond
